<body>
<p>Reports the value of <code>@DefaultValue</code> if it cannot be converted to the specified type of parameter.</p>
<p><b>Example:</b></p>
<pre><code>
  @GET
  @Path("/{n}")
  public String get(@PathParam("n") @DefaultValue("<b>III</b>") int n) { // Error: Cannot convert 'III' to int
  }
</code></pre>
</body>
</html>
